{"tid":1922152,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】湯漢斯澳洲中招 Marvel大作《上氣》拍攝或受影響","createTime":"2020-03-12T11:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:16:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3db5328985693c1dd978b471048608a5a5a5e4bf","tid":1922152,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:39:09.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡金像影帝湯漢斯（Tom Hanks）透過IG向外公佈，他與老婆影星麗達韋遜（Rita Wilson）亦證實患上武漢肺炎。二人發佈聲明稱他們在澳洲拍攝新片時確診感染武漢肺炎。而除了其拍攝中的貓王電影要停機，現正同樣身處澳洲拍攝Marvel大作《上氣》（Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings）的梁朝偉或同樣受影響。<br />\n<br />\nMarvel電影《上氣》由劉思慕主演，梁朝偉更飾演反派滿大人。而近日劉思慕都有更新自己的拍攝情況，雖然未見拍檔如Awkwafina，但他亦有表示自己注重衛生，更上載了戴口罩的相片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/nbEPDxvDjCIQKBUPyJgOZDdJ1Oc=/346x346/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/4GS3JM4VBFOWOAILIM3WDTYCMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FnbEPDxvDjCIQKBUPyJgOZDdJ1Oc%3D%2F346x346%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F4GS3JM4VBFOWOAILIM3WDTYCMI.jpg&h=64658dce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ed67aacf5f88d0c146cca92489a7809484c5a4c","tid":1922152,"uid":97340,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"正式上氣唔接下氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cd7a905c8bc02fe69794728f898012c5894bf5","tid":1922152,"uid":77180,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"肺炎奇俠"},{"pid":"9d210a80daceeb8b1bb196e99b17352861d6e498","tid":1922152,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"個肺變左公文袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e1ef7d49598a70d355feff88ab1741606d44b9","tid":1922152,"uid":188282,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:4